rc=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d4b7d8b129c20f68e9ebd80d80bd91ab45e53de2","tid":1427854,"uid":167435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:01:15.000Z","msg":"推~~！"},{"pid":"b74d058547e6a3a2229824adb818b28aa82cb276","tid":1427854,"uid":167435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:08:59.000Z","msg":"推呀屌"},{"pid":"0b6cd70687f10e219d88fb005b554b7ee6466c3b","tid":1427854,"uid":167435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:09:53.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"8f28b344e21785e418753c1eafc85645f478cb60","tid":1427854,"uid":167435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:13:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">更新 14:10</span></strong></span><br />\n關博士喺啱啱 13:22 嘅時候出咗第三篇文章，講述對人類呼吸系統嘅禍害，嚴重者<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>因為催淚彈被射入屋，致吸入高濃度毒氣而死亡</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n===<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Dr.Kwan/photos/a.688252451369682/1164126980448891/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDr.Kwan%2Fphotos%2Fa.688252451369682%2F1164126980448891%2F&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=9e4a606f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Dr.Kwan/photos/a.688252451369682/1164126980448891/</a><br />\n關家倫 中醫學博士<br />\n08/08/2019, 13:22<br />\n<br />\n《催淚彈是毒性極強的化學武器 3：呼吸系統篇》<br />\n<br />\n近日警方再公佈於8月5日僅一日內發射800枚催淚彈。新聞報導不少催淚彈落在住宅附近，繼之前講述催淚毒氣（CS毒氣）對皮膚（ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2KvSnOX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KvSnOX&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=27c3660d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2KvSnOX</a> ）和消化系統（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Yw8Z3e）的損害，今日再講述對呼吸系統的影響。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Yw8Z3e%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E6%90%8D%E5%AE%B3%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E5%86%8D%E8%AC%9B%E8%BF%B0%E5%B0%8D%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E3%80%82&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=a4374585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2Yw8Z3e）的損害，今日再講述對呼吸系統的影響。</a><br />\n<br />\n根據流行病學和公共衞生醫學期刊的綜述文章和系統回顧(Systematic Review) 指出，吸入催淚毒氣後呼吸系統的症狀可在即時至三星期內發生。<span style=\"color: orange;\">短期出現的不適有咳嗽、呼吸困難、胸悶、咽喉灼痛等等。較嚴重的症狀有化學性肺炎、支氣管收縮、喉梗阻等等</span>。而在吸入毒氣的人群肺功能測試顯示，婦女出現呼吸氣道阻塞的情況比較嚴重。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而反覆吸入催淚毒氣的人群往後較易患上慢性支氣管炎</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n另外亦有案例在吸入毒氣後患上反應性氣道功能障礙症候群 (Reactive Airway Dysfunction Syndrome)，其臨床表現為長期出現類哮喘和氣管過敏。該案例的不適持續兩年而且需要每天服藥治療。<br />\n<br />\n而最嚴重的案例出現在巴林的示威活動當中，催淚彈直接射入一名中年男子家中，他吸入大量毒氣後出現呼吸衰竭，送到當地醫院一日後不治身亡。<br />\n<br />\n以上所述症狀總結於附圖列表。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C2rWDyO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC2rWDyO.jpg&h=ad5beb4f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"517aa0ebdb647a58aa8dbbcea9d861d5df9960c3","tid":1427854,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:16:53.000Z","msg":"吸完 日日都好攰 晚晚都早訓"},{"pid":"7baaea3e441a7e143c020e58fd25762bb9591c11","tid":1427854,"uid":167435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"517aa0ebdb647a58aa8dbbcea9d861d5df9960c3","tid":1427854,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:16:53.000Z","msg":"吸完 日日都好攰 晚晚都早訓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:18:20.000Z","msg":"我伴侶都係咁，吸完啲生理時鐘亂晒<br />\n又食得唔好<br />\n我自己就成日想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbeface9cc9d4104e2c63e13fb90eb110414e129","tid":1427854,"uid":176121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958c93a378c6adc237eef503927ac90ade252a72","tid":1427854,"uid":167435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:31:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42012021e9a178c520efc91687302b43c03cf1c8","tid":1427854,"uid":167435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:52:39.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"afbf46a0c15fc5ff52a42c389e150c7cff212724","tid":1427854,"uid":167435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:25:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c396c077f5d005b839988733373948082480b4fc","tid":1427854,"uid":75684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:41:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"770b0569f34af5ef9631842cc6ee030b278a6d51","tid":1427854,"uid":167435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b01c67c592012d379746f53d36f73334354672","tid":1427854,"uid":167435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba71b89e3363cf99301cdb4a1cde686046b4e5c","tid":1427854,"uid":167435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p